lead_paragraph: Kelsey Lang scored 12 points, including eight on a crucial second-quarter run, and No. 8 Texas won its 25th game this season with a 76-55 victory over Texas Tech on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 8 Texas Wins 25th Game, 76-55 Over Texas Tech
